{
  "name": "muse",
  "displayName": "Muse",
  "version": "0.4.0",
  "description": "muse is publish tool for bid",
  "categories": [
    "Other"
  ],
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "http://gitlab.100credit.cn/fed/muse.git"
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "author": "hec9527",
  "publisher": "hec9527",
  "main": "./dist/extension.js",
  "scripts": {
    "build": "yarn run build:webview && yarn run build:extension",
    "build:extension": "cross-env NODE_ENV=production webpack --mode production --config ./script/webpack.extension.config.js",
    "build:webview": "cross-env NODE_ENV=production webpack --mode production --config ./script/webpack.config.js",
    "clear": "rm -rf dist",
    "compile": "yarn run clear && yarn run build",
    "dev": "yarn run dev:webview & yarn run dev:extension",
    "dev:extension": "cross-env NODE_ENV=production webpack -w --config ./script/webpack.extension.config.js",
    "dev:webview": "cross-env NODE_ENV=development webpack -w --config ./script/webpack.config.js",
    "lint": "eslint src --ext ts,tsx",
    "pub": "yarn lint && vsce publish",
    "vscode:prepublish": "npm run lint && yarn run compile",
    "vsix": "vsce package -o muse-$npm_package_version.vsix && code --install-extension muse-$npm_package_version.vsix"
  },
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "muse.webview",
        "title": "webview",
        "category": "Muse"
      }
    ],
    "configuration": {
      "title": "Muse",
      "properties": {
        "muse.autoOpenLog": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "description": "发布成功后自动在浏览器中打开日志"
        },
        "muse.publishAction": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "default",
          "enum": [
            "default",
            "openInBrowse",
            "detectLogo",
            "none"
          ],
          "markdownDescription": "### 发布成功后的操作\n- `default` 打开提示，每次发布自行决定\n- `openInBrowse` 在浏览器中查看日志\n- `detectLogo` 自动探测发布日志，成功失败后系统通知提示（实验功能）\n- `none` 不进行任何操作"
        },
        "muse.logKeyWord": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "default": [
            "md5对比失败"
          ],
          "title": "日志关键字检查",
          "markdownDescription": "### 日志关键字检查\n当日志中出现以下关键字时，提示错误"
        },
        "muse.publishResultNoticeType": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "integration",
            "system"
          ],
          "default": "integration",
          "markdownDescription": "### 发布结果通知方式\n- `integration` 使用vscode内置通知，在系统打开勿扰模式依然可用\n- `system` 使用系统通知，系统通知优先级更高，在vscode后台时依然可见"
        },
        "muse.hideDisabledFilter": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "markdownDescription": "### 隐藏被禁用的过滤器\n页面选择的过滤器是按照页面首字母编排的，如果某个首字母的页面不存在，该字母将会被禁用，隐藏没用的过滤器可以减少不必要内容，在小窗模式或者放大模式下不至于超出屏幕边界"
        },
        "muse.autoOpenQuickPublishModal": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "快速发布时，选择发布内容后自动打开发布弹窗"
        }
      }
    },
    "keybindings": [
      {
        "key": "ctrl+p ctrl+p",
        "mac": "ctrl+p ctrl+p",
        "command": "muse.webview"
      }
    ]
  },
  "activationEvents": [
    "onCommand:muse.webview",
    "workspaceContains:src/p"
  ],
  "dependencies": {
    "@bairong/lib-util": "^2.0.0",
    "@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core": "^1.2.36",
    "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons": "^5.15.4",
    "@fortawesome/react-fontawesome": "^0.1.15",
    "axios": "^0.21.1",
    "classnames": "^2.3.1",
    "node-notifier": "^10.0.1",
    "react": "^17.0.2",
    "react-dom": "^17.0.2",
    "react-redux": "^7.2.4",
    "redux": "^4.1.1",
    "socket.io-client": "^2.5.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@babel/core": "^7.14.8",
    "@babel/preset-env": "^7.14.8",
    "@babel/preset-react": "^7.14.5",
    "@babel/preset-typescript": "^7.15.0",
    "@types/glob": "^7.1.3",
    "@types/mocha": "^8.0.4",
    "@types/node": "^12.11.7",
    "@types/node-notifier": "^8.0.2",
    "@types/react": "^17.0.14",
    "@types/react-dom": "^17.0.9",
    "@types/socket.io-client": "^1.4.36",
    "@types/vscode": "^1.53.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin": "^4.28.4",
    "@typescript-eslint/parser": "^4.28.4",
    "babel-loader": "^8.2.2",
    "cross-env": "^7.0.3",
    "css-loader": "^6.2.0",
    "eslint": "^7.15.0",
    "eslint-plugin-prettier": "^4.0.0",
    "eslint-plugin-react": "^7.24.0",
    "glob": "^7.1.6",
    "less": "^4.1.1",
    "less-loader": "^10.0.1",
    "prettier": "^2.7.1",
    "prettier-plugin-packagejson": "^2.2.18",
    "style-loader": "^3.2.1",
    "stylelint": "^14.4.0",
    "stylelint-config-prettier": "^9.0.3",
    "stylelint-config-rational-order": "^0.1.2",
    "stylelint-config-standard": "^24.0.0",
    "stylelint-order": "^5.0.0",
    "ts-loader": "^9.2.5",
    "typescript": "^4.3.4",
    "vscode-test": "1.5.2",
    "webpack": "^5.45.1",
    "webpack-cli": "^4.7.2"
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=10",
    "vscode": "^1.53.0"
  },
  "icon": "logo.png"
}
